o if you were gone.\r\n\r\n1182\r\n01:55:48,146 --> 01:55:51,581\r\nI'm also thinking I'm gonna\r\nhave the boys over tomorrow.\r\n\r\n1183\r\n01:55:55,653 --> 01:55:58,281\r\nWell, you sure do know\r\nhow to cook chicken.\r\n\r\n1184\r\n01:55:58,455 --> 01:55:59,786\r\nWell, thank you.\r\n\r\n1185\r\n01:56:00,057 --> 01:56:02,821\r\nThis is one delicious treat, ma'am,\r\nbefore I go to work.\r\n\r\n1186\r\n01:56:03,060 --> 01:56:04,493\r\nI'm glad you're enjoying it.\r\n\r\n1187\r\n01:56:04,929 --> 01:56:07,193\r\nHey, Brutal, you gonna hog\r\nall them taters?\r\n\r\n1188\r\n01:56:07,398 --> 01:56:09,958\r\nYes, I am.\r\nHarry, you want some potatoes?\r\n\r\n1189\r\n01:56:10,167 --> 01:56:12,397\r\n- Come on, now.\r\n- What?\r\n\r\n1190\r\n01:56:12,570 --> 01:56:15,334\r\nSoon we'll just see your feet\r\nsticking out of there, Brutus.\r\n\r\n1191\r\n01:56:15,539 --> 01:56:17,905\r\nYou all saw what he did to the mouse.\r\n\r\n1192\r\n01:56:20,744 --> 01:56:23,144\r\nI could've gone the rest of the day\r\nwithout you bringing that up.\r\n\r\n1193\r\n01:56:23,347 --> 01:56:25,144\r\nI could've gone\r\nthe rest of the year.\r\n\r\n1194\r\n01:56:25,583 --> 01:56:27,414\r\nHe did the same thing to me.\r\n\r\n1195\r\n01:56:27,785 --> 01:56:29,844\r\nHe put his hands on me.\r\n\r\n1196\r\n01:56:30,621 --> 01:56:32,748\r\nHe took my bladder infection away.\r\n\r\n1197\r\n01:56:37,627 --> 01:56:41,154\r\nIt's true. When he came home that day,\r\nhe was...\r\n\r\n1198\r\n01:56:42,699 --> 01:56:44,098\r\n...all better.\r\n\r\n1199\r\n01:56:45,602 --> 01:56:48,537\r\nOh, now, wait.\r\nYou're talking about...\r\n\r\n1200\r\n01:56:48,738 --> 01:56:50,399\r\n...an authentic healing?\r\n\r\n1201\r\n01:56:51,774 --> 01:56:53,139\r\nA praise-Jesus miracle?\r\n\r\n1202\r\n01:56:53,843 --> 01:56:55,071\r\nI am.\r\n\r\n1203\r\n01:56:55,979 --> 01:56:57,571\r\nOh, yeah.\r\n\r\n1204\r\n01:56:57,747 --> 01:57:00,648\r\nWell, if you say it, I accept it.\r\n\r\n1205\r\n01:57:01,618 --> 01:5