> 00:40:30,180\r\nYou don't ever throw the switch\r\non a man without that.\r\n\r\n431\r\n00:40:33,124 --> 00:40:34,955\r\nHush up there, Toot.\r\n\r\n432\r\n00:40:37,796 --> 00:40:39,855\r\nGetting screwed.\r\n\r\n433\r\n00:40:40,832 --> 00:40:42,766\r\nI'm getting the cap.\r\n\r\n434\r\n00:40:46,805 --> 00:40:48,397\r\nArlen Bitterbuck...\r\n\r\n435\r\n00:40:48,606 --> 00:40:51,973\r\n...electricity shall be passed through\r\nyour body until you are dead...\r\n\r\n436\r\n00:40:52,210 --> 00:40:54,440\r\n...in accordance with state law.\r\n\r\n437\r\n00:40:54,879 --> 00:40:57,245\r\nGod have mercy on your soul.\r\n\r\n438\r\n00:40:58,550 --> 00:40:59,983\r\nAmen.\r\n\r\n439\r\n00:41:02,387 --> 00:41:03,513\r\nRoll on two.\r\n\r\n440\r\n00:41:07,559 --> 00:41:09,083\r\nAnd that's that.\r\n\r\n441\r\n00:41:12,029 --> 00:41:15,396\r\nI'm frying! I'm frying!\r\n\r\n442\r\n00:41:17,101 --> 00:41:20,229\r\nI'm a done tom turkey!\r\n\r\n443\r\n00:41:21,905 --> 00:41:24,806\r\nThis is a shocking experience!\r\n\r\n444\r\n00:41:25,476 --> 00:41:28,570\r\nOne of the witnesses\r\nshowed up a day early.\r\n\r\n445\r\n00:41:35,586 --> 00:41:38,316\r\nLet's do it again,\r\nand let's get it right this time.\r\n\r\n446\r\n00:41:38,522 --> 00:41:40,922\r\nGet that idiot out of the chair.\r\n\r\n447\r\n00:42:41,016 --> 00:42:45,646\r\nDo you think if a man sincerely\r\nrepents on what he done wrong...\r\n\r\n448\r\n00:42:46,688 --> 00:42:50,180\r\n...that he might get to go back to\r\nthe time that was happiest for him...\r\n\r\n449\r\n00:42:50,792 --> 00:42:52,555\r\n...and live there forever?\r\n\r\n450\r\n00:42:54,963 --> 00:42:56,988\r\nCould that be what heaven's like?\r\n\r\n451\r\n00:42:58,400 --> 00:43:00,994\r\nI just about believe that very thing.\r\n\r\n452\r\n00:43:07,042 --> 00:43:10,341\r\nHad me a young wife when I was 18.\r\n\r\n453\r\n00:43:11,012 --> 00:43:15,676\r\nSpent our first summer in the mountains.\r\nMade love every night.\r\n\r\n454\r\n00:43:16,351 --> 00:43:19,479\r\nAnd she'd lie there after...\r\n\r\n455\r\n00:43:20,422 --> 00:43:22,788\r\n...bare-breasted in the firelight.\r\n\r\n456\r\n00:43:24,058 --> 00:43:27,255\r\nAnd we'd talk sometimes\r\ntill the sun come up.\r\n\r\n457\r\n00:43:30,531 --> 00:43:32,795\r\nThat was my best time.\r\n\r\n458\r\n00:43:52,820 --> 00:43:54,481\r\nIt'll be fine.\r\n\r\n459\r\n00:43:55,723 --> 00:43:57,384\r\nYou'll do fine.\r\n\r\n460\r\n00:44:33,493 --> 00:44:37,224\r\nArlen Bitterbuck, electricity shall\r\nnow be passed through your body...\r\n\r\n461\r\n00:44:37,430 --> 00:44:41,491\r\n...until you are dead,\r\nin accordance with state law.\r\n\r\n462\r\n00:44:41,701 --> 00:44:44,101\r\nGod have mercy on your soul.\r\n\r\n463\r\n00:45:03,822 --> 00:45:05,016\r\nRoll on two.\r\n\r\n464\r\n00:45:49,810 --> 00:45:51,334\r\nAgain.\r\n\r\n465\r\n00:45:57,517 --> 00:45:59,212\r\n<i>Adi�s, chief.</i>\r\n\r\n466\r\n00:45:59,586 --> 00:46:04,182\r\nDrop us a card from hell.\r\nLet us know if it's hot enough.\r\n\r\n467\r\n00:46:06,793 --> 00:46:08,920\r\nHe's paid what he owed.\r\n\r\n468\r\n00:46:09,329 --> 00:46:11,627\r\nHe's square with the house again...\r\n\r\n469\r\n00:46:11,832 --> 00:46:14,528\r\n...so keep your goddamn hands off him.\r\n\r\n470\r\n00:46:34,687 --> 00:46:36,518\r\nWhat's up his ass?\r\n\r\n471\r\n00:46:36,722 --> 00:46:38,019\r\nYou.\r\n\r\n472\r\n00:46:39,025 --> 00:46:41,619\r\nAlways. You, Percy.\r\n\r\n473\r\n00:46:42,228 --> 00:46:45,391\r\nYou gotta hate the new boy?\r\nThat the way it is around here?\r\n\r\n474\r\n00:46:47,366 --> 00:46:50,665\r\nWhy don't you just move on?\r\nTake that job at Briar Ridge?\r\n\r\n475\r\n00:46:51,570 --> 00:46:54,038\r\nOh, yeah. I know all about it.\r\n\r\n476\r\n00:46:54,540 --> 00:46:57,839\r\nSounds to me like a pretty good job.\r\n\r\n477\r\n00:46:59,211 --> 00:47:02,669\r\nI might just take it too,\r\nsoon as you put me out front.\r\n\r\n478\r\n00:47:03,816 --> 00:47:05,249\r\nYeah, you heard me.\r\n\r\n479\r\n00